<p>Code:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-go-text-template" data-lang="go-text-template"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">quote</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">&gt;</span><span class="cp">}}</span><span class="x">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="x">Don&#39;t believe everything you read on the Internet.
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="x"></span><span class="cp">{{</span><span class="err">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">paige</span><span class="err">/</span><span class="nx">quote</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">&gt;</span><span class="cp">}}</span><span class="x">
</span></span></span></code></pre></div><p>Result:</p>




















































    


<figure class="     paige-figure " >
    

    

    <div class="text-center"><blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
Don't believe everything you read on the Internet.</blockquote></div>

    

    

    
</figure>


<hr>
<p>Code:</p>
